She said, \'93Ned, I\'92m not asking you to reveal anything that\'92s classified. I\'92m merely trying to understand exactly what happened.\'94\
He seemed relieved, then nervous.\
She said simply, \'93The notes we have indicated that someone died. Did someone die?\'94\
He said, \'93Yes. No. We\'92re not sure.\'94\
\'93Was there a specific person or persons who died?\'94\
\'93There was one specific person who may or may not have died.\'94\
\'93Is there a body?\'94\
